text: Milpitas () is a city in Santa Clara County, California. The population was 80,273 at the 2020 census. It shares borders with San Jose to the south and Fremont to the north. Milpitas is part of Silicon Valley and has many technology companies. ==References== Category:1954 establishments in California Category:Settlements in Santa Clara County, California Category:Cities in California Category:Cities in the San Francisco Bay Area
